'''Dassault Systèmes GEOVIA''' is a set of [[geologic modeling]] and [[mining engineering]] [[software]] applications developed by the French engineering software company [[Dassault Systèmes]]. Formerly known as Gemcom, the company was founded in 1985 as a spin-off from by mining consultants SRK Consulting, with headquarters in [[Vancouver, British Columbia]], [[Canada]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://schnitgercorp.com/2012/08/06/gemcom-and-geovia-a-tale-of-two-brands/|title=Gemcom and GEOVIA, a tale of two brands - Schnitger Corporation|date=6 August 2012|publisher=}}</ref>

